1. *Ponoć* je vrijeme kada većina ljudi spava. (Midnight is the time when most people sleep.)
2. Došao sam kući tačno u *ponoć*. (I came home exactly at midnight.)
3. Žurka je trajala do *ponoći*. (The party lasted until midnight.)
4. Trebalo bi da idemo kući prije *poneć* ako želimo da uhvatimo prvi autobus. (We should go home before midnight if we want to catch the first bus.)
5. *Ponoć* je prošla, a oni još uvijek nisu stigli. (Midnight has passed, and they still haven't arrived.)
6. Uzbuđenje je dostiglo vrhunac u *ponoć* kada je otkriveno ime pobjednika. (Excitement reached its peak at midnight when the winner's name was revealed.)
7. Vidjela sam te sinoć u *ponoći* kako hodaš ulicom. (I saw you last night at midnight walking down the street.)
8. Većina noćnih klubova radi do *ponoći*. (Most nightclubs work until midnight.)
9. Nije zdravo ostajati budan do *ponoći* svake noći. (It's not healthy to stay up until midnight every night.)
10. *Ponoć* je bila magična kada su se njihove oči srele prvi put. (Midnight was magical when their eyes met for the first time.)